[CodexICE X2CharacterTemplate]
strCharacterName="Codex ICE"
strAcquiredText="The Intrusion Countermeasure, or ICE, is a Codex that is specialized on taking down single enemies. It will aggressively teleport into flanks to cause heavy damage with its Boltcaster." 
[CodexAdvent X2CharacterTemplate]
strCharacterName="ADVENT Codex"
strAcquiredText="When dropships are too slow, ADVENT will teleport onto the battlefield by Codex. This Codex will draw any enemy fire at point of entry to it, dodging it with inhuman agility." 
[CodexSplitter X2CharacterTemplate]
strCharacterName="Codex Splitter"
strAcquiredText="Splitters roam on their own because they are able to rapidly chain clone into an instant army if they are unhindered for even a moment." 
[CodexBomber X2CharacterTemplate]
