strAcquiredText="Bomber Codices use an empowered version of the Psi Bomb that doesn't have a cooldown. They can also use this ability on reveal." 
[CodexM4 X2CharacterTemplate]
strCharacterName="Codex Prime"
strAcquiredText="Prime Codices use an empowered version of the Psi Bomb that doesn't have a cooldown. They also split on reveal and can activate a personal shield when in danger." 

[SpectreM4 X2CharacterTemplate]
strCharacterName="Spectre Prime"
strAcquiredText="Like all Primes, the Prime Spectre can react to incoming fire with instant reactions." 

[Shoggoth X2CharacterTemplate]
strCharacterName="Shoggoth" 
strAcquiredText="ADVENT started to mix Faceless disguised as Troopers into their regiments. The resistance calls them Shoggoth because of their black and oily appearance." 

[GatekeeperM4 X2CharacterTemplate]
strCharacterName="Gatekeeper Prime" 
strAcquiredText="Gatekeeper Prime are devastating laser platforms. They don't have psionic abilities, but will charge up whenever hit." 

[AndromedonM4 X2CharacterTemplate]
strCharacterName="Andromedon Prime" 
strAcquiredText="Andromedon Prime use heavy acid weaponry. Like all Primes, they have instant reactions to incoming fire." 

[AndromedonRobotM4 X2CharacterTemplate]
strCharacterName="Andromedon Prime Shell"
strAcquiredText="Like all Primes, this Prime Shell does have instant reactions to incoming fire." 

[ArchonM4 X2CharacterTemplate]
