[ArchonMelee X2CharacterTemplate]
strCharacterName="Archon Valkyrie" 
strAcquiredText="The Valkyrie is melee-only variants of the Archon. She wields a lifedraining staff and has a unique area of effect ability that causes a mass panic around her." 
[ArchonSentinel X2CharacterTemplate]
strCharacterName="Archon Sentinel" 
